    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#一、安装在文件夹中打开终端的右键菜单<br><figure class="highlight"><figcaption><span>codeblock %&#125; #apt-get install nautilus-open-terminal &#123;% endcodeblock %&#125; ```</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#27880;&#38144;&#19968;&#19979;&#23601;&#21487;&#20197;&#29992;&#20102;&#10;#&#20108;&#12289;&#24320;&#21551;root&#36134;&#25143;&#10;&#35774;&#32622;root&#36134;&#21495;&#23494;&#30721;&#10;``` &#123;% codeblock %&#125; #passwd root &#123;% endcodeblock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>编辑配置文件<br> <figure class="highlight"><figcaption><span>codeblock %&#125; #gedit</span><a href="/etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf">&#123;% endcodeblock %&#125; ```</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#22686;&#21152;&#36825;&#34892;&#20195;&#30721; &#10;``` &#123;% codeblock %&#125; greeter-show-manual-login=true &#123;% endcodeblock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>重启，就可以在登陆界面输入root账号密码登陆了</p>
